claim: The Voice awards 100,000 dollars and a record deal.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Per 100.000 dollari ti ammazzo  (  literally I will kill you for 100,000 dollars or 100,000 dollars for killing you , internationally released as Vengeance is Mine , For One Hundred Thousand Dollars for a Killing and One Hundred Thousand Dollars Per Killing  )  is a 1967 Italian Spaghetti Western film .
